race.comment: FLOREY (5) has gone to a new level this time in and looks very hard to stop. Is drawn to advantage for Toeroek and looks perfectly placed out to the mile. Very hard to beat. MELLIFLUENT (4) keeps knocking on the door, narrowly denied again last time. Stays at the mile, where he does his best work, and draws to get the A1 spot. Have to take seriously. MAGARTEN (3) has mixed his form this prep but gets things going again last time when closing strongly into third. Loves this trip and should be nearing his peak. Can threaten. SECOND FIX (10) is building nicely and gets a nice pull at the weights over FLOREY. Ready to fire third-up, though is drawn horribly. Needs some luck. CHUR NIBBLE (11) gave another bold sight last start but couldn't match the winner late. Drops back to the mile off a month in-between and is drawn to advantage. Will be in this for a very long way.
